OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777651869
OL,3,CProbe launched into officer who
OL,4,CTasered teenager before he was hit by
OL,5,Ccar
OL,7,FA police officer is being investigated
OL,8,Ffor tasering a teenager from Weston-
OL,9,Fsuper-Mare who was then hit by a car
OL,10,Fand killed on the M5.
OL,12,FLogan Smith, 18, was being taken to
OL,13,Fhospital in an ambulance at 11pm on
OL,14,FNovember 30 last year when the vehicle
OL,15,Fhad to pull over on the hard shoulder
OL,16,Fof the M5 northbound carriageway, due
OL,17,Fto the concerns of staff on board.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
