OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777651869
OL,3,CProbe launched into officer who
OL,4,CTasered teenager before he was hit by
OL,5,Ccar
OL,7,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct (IOPC) said Mr Smith got out
OL,9,Fof the ambulance near the junction for
OL,10,FWeston-super-Mare and entered the live
OL,11,Flanes of the motorway.
OL,13,FAn Avon and Somerset Police officer
OL,14,Fattempted to engage with Mr Smith on
OL,15,Fthe motorway, then discharged their
OL,16,FTaser, causing him to fall to the
OL,17,Fground, the IOPC said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777651869
OL,3,CProbe launched into officer who
OL,4,CTasered teenager before he was hit by
OL,5,Ccar
OL,7,FA misconduct probe has now been
OL,8,Flaunched by the watchdog, looking at
OL,9,Fwhether the tactical options,
OL,10,Fincluding the use of Taser by the
OL,11,Fofficer, were proportionate and
OL,12,Freasonable and if relevant training
OL,13,Fand policies were followed.
OL,15,FIOPC director Derrick Campbell said:
OL,16,F"Our thoughts and sympathies remain
OL,17,Fwith Logan's family and friends.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777651869
OL,3,CProbe launched into officer who
OL,4,CTasered teenager before he was hit by
OL,5,Ccar
OL,7,F"We understand the profound impact
OL,8,Flosing Logan has had on his loved ones
OL,9,Fand we want to reassure everyone that
OL,10,Fwe are carrying out a thorough and
OL,11,Findependent investigation into the
OL,12,Fcircumstances leading to his death.
OL,14,F"As part of our investigation we have
OL,15,Fcommissioned a report from an
OL,16,Findependent Taser expert.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777651869
OL,3,CProbe launched into officer who
OL,4,CTasered teenager before he was hit by
OL,5,Ccar
OL,7,F"We have shared that report with
OL,8,FLogan's family and Avon and Somerset
OL,9,FPolice and we are considering its
OL,10,Ffindings as part of our final
OL,11,Fdeterminations.
OL,13,F"We continue to update Logan's family,
OL,14,Fthe force and the coroner on the
OL,15,Fprogress of our investigation."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
