OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777651869
OL,3,CProbe launched into officer who
OL,4,CTasered teenager before he was hit by
OL,5,Ccar
OL,7,FThe IOPC said the potential misconduct
OL,8,Frelates to the officer's decision to
OL,9,Fuse their Taser, and it is also
OL,10,Falleged the officer failed to carry
OL,11,Fout a pre-discharge check of their
OL,12,FTaser, as required under Avon and
OL,13,FSomerset Police protocol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
